In this case, animals could be excluded.
But even if consciousness was not to depend on language, it would certainly influence it, so that animal consciousness, whatever the way it is produced, would probably differ much from most of our state of consciousness.
That is why it is so difficult to determine what the consciousness of other animals may look like.
